===============================
 Python extension to memcached
===============================

.. contents::
..
    1  Description
    2  Dependencies
    3  To do
    4  Known Bugs

Description
===========

Python extension to memcached, build on top of libmemcache. API very similar to
memcache.py, except for some return codes which follow libmemcache conventions.

Dependencies
============

- Python
- libmemcache (using version 1.4.0.rc2, not sure which is required

To do
=====

- use mc_req_add_ref to avoid copy of key

Known Bugs
==========

- set_servers with the wrong port number causes a segfault (in libmemcache). See commented
  out testing code in test.py.

